summary: Hey do you have any good killing eve accounts on Twitter? I’m new and I wanna follow good people:)
question: Hey do you have any good killing eve accounts on Twitter? I’m new and I wanna follow good people:)
answer:
i am actually doing a podcast, and we have a twitter that is exclusively killing eve called @killingevefans. i pretty much get all my killing eve content from that. my mom runs it, and she’s very on top of it.

@villanelleslut is great, @killingevenews, @spillingeve is another fan podcast.

im not really on twitter as much as tumblr but when i am i love those accounts. i hope this was helpful!!
